# Dedicated Anthropic API key for blacksmith (PRD §8 / §12 decision 3).
# This is NOT your interactive Claude Code / subscription auth — blacksmith's
# programmatic usage meters against this key only, keeping its spend isolated
# and predictable. Copy this file to `.env`, fill in the key, and never commit `.env`.
BLACKSMITH_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
